{"tid":2043492,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"有玩過陰陽大戰記神操機嘅入","createTime":"2020-05-30T12:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T09:44:11.000Z","uid":359634,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"34eb4e041fd6ae048e72c66cbd92031f442e8032","tid":2043492,"uid":359634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T12:45:59.000Z","msg":"話說前幾日睇到有個post討論陰陽大戰記呢套卡通片<br />\n令我諗返起以前細個嗰陣玩神操機嘅回憶(部機好耐之前已經開唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n如果你以前都有玩過神操機同埋有玩到去最後一關(唔肯定係唔係最後一關，因為我過極都過唔到)嘅話，就會知道嗰一關係一棵大樹，隻BOSS係一條龍，無記錯嘅話佢有成1000血。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n有冇人知道隻嘢究竟係點打，我明明已經chok心 體 技 chok到完美，有時仲會有機會chok到巨大化(不過我以前細個玩咗咁耐都唔係太肯定點樣先可以觸發到chok巨大化)<br />\nBandai好似以前為咗跟返三位主角部機進化咗嘅劇情，出咗進化神操機玩具，不過我無買，不過唔係太肯定關唔關事"},{"pid":"2011267d1519532e664398903b3cf71ef80e4345","tid":2043492,"uid":27172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T17:09:47.000Z","msg":"強化版嗰部極神操機當年香港係無代理版<br />\n有都係日版炒到天價"},{"pid":"c8b5b561965fbb96b2ff0400c0571b44230b3eb5","tid":2043492,"uid":213017,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:41:12.000Z","msg":"開唔到機了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yR4skJj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyR4skJj.png&h=56b3811d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2639f3fb554c3755de423719a03a16fa6090cf9","tid":2043492,"uid":359634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8b5b561965fbb96b2ff0400c0571b44230b3eb5","tid":2043492,"uid":213017,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:41:12.000Z","msg":"開唔到機了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yR4skJj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyR4skJj.png&h=56b3811d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1